texts.content: {"text":"18. U kunda surga puflanur va \n sizlar to`p-to`p bo`lib kelursiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"30. Bas, tatib ko`ringlar, sizlarga azobdan boshqa hech narsani ziyoda qilmasmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"33. Va yangi bo`yi yetgan bir xil yoshdagi qizlar bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,57]}]}

{"text":"35. U yerda bekorchi va yolg`on gaplarni eshitmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,53]}]}

{"text":"37. U, osmonlar, yer va ularning orasidagi barcha narsalarning Robbi, Rohmandir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"Uning huzurida hech kim xitob qilishga qodir bo`lmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,53]}]}

{"text":"38. O`sha kunda Ruh va \nfarishtalar saf bo`lib turar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,54]}]}

{"text":"Rohman izn berganlar va to`g`ri \nso`zlaganlardan o`zgalar hech gapira olmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"39. U haq kundir. Kim xohlasa, \no`z Robbiga qaytar yo`l oladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,63]}]}

{"text":"40. Albatta, Biz sizlarni yaqin kelajakdagi azobdan qo`rqitdik. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"U kunda, har kishi qo`li taqdim qilgan narsaga nazar soladir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"12. Agar shundoq bo`lsa, bu hasratiy qaytish-ku!  derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"13. Albatta, u(qiyomat) bir qichqiriqdan boshqa narsa emas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"16. Qachonki Robbisi unga Muqaddas Tuva vodiysida nido qildi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"19. Va seni Robbingga hidoyat qilsam, shoyadki (undan) qo`rqsang, degin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,74]}]}

{"text":"24. Va, men sizlarning eng oliy Robbingizman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"25. Bas, Alloh uni avvalgi va oxirgi gunohlari uchun azobga oldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"26. Albatta, bunda U zotdan \nqo`rqqanlar uchun ibrat bordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,60]}]}

{"text":"27. Sizlarni yaratish qiyinmi yoki \nU zot bino qilgan osmonnimi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"28. Uning shiftini yuqori ko`tardi va bekami-ko`st, mustahkam qilib qo`ydi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"30. Va undan so`ng yerni tuxum shaklida qildi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,46]}]}

{"text":"40. Va ammo, kim Robbisining maqomidan qo`rqqan ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"xuddi, bu dunyoda bir kecha yoki kunduzdan boshqa turmaganga o`xsharlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,72]}]}

{"text":"4. Yoki nasihat olar va mav'iza unga manfaat berar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"7. U poklanmasa, seni hech kim malomat qilmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,46]}]}

{"text":"17. Insonga la'nat bo`lsin, \nuning kofirligi qandoq shiddatli bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,69]}]}

{"text":"23. Yo`q, undoq emas! \nU o`ziga U zot qilgan amrni bajarmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"32. Sizlarga va chorvalaringizga manfaat va lazzat bo`lsin, deb.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"37. U kunda ulardan har bir shaxsni ovora qiluvchi o`z ishi bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"40. U kunda bir chehralar borki, \nularni g`ubor bosgan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,55]}]}
